The '''2003 Milan–San Remo''' was the 94th edition of the [[classic cycle races|monument classic]] [[Milan–San Remo]] and was won by Italian [[Paolo Bettini]] of [[Quick Step-Davitamon]]. The race was run on March 22, 2003 and the {{convert|297|km|mi}} was covered in 6 hours, 44 minutes and 43 seconds.

